how_to_use:
How to use
Apply Darphin Stimulskin Plus Absolute Renewal Eye & Lip Contour Cream 15ml (0.51fl oz) a small amount of product around the eye and lip area. Use your fingertips to distribute the product and then use the massaging tool to work the product onto the skin. Lastly, wipe the tool clean after each application, and then rinse and dry it before storing. 
Step 1: Work the tool under the eyes with back and forth movements. Repeat three times to help improve microcirculation and reduce puffiness. Then glide back and forth along the inner corner to help reduce dark circles. Repeat the movement three times; 
Step 2: Perform a lifting movement from under the eyebrow, across the arch and towards the temple. Repeat the massage three times in order to help improve firmness and tone over time;
Step 3: Use the tool to work the temple, drawing the figure of number "eight";
Step 4: Rub the tool back and forth on the hem of the upper and lower lip to help minimize the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles over time. Repeat three times;
Step 5: Work the tool with lifting and circular motions, going up and down following the nasolabial fold. Repeat the massage three times in order to help improve results;
Step 6: Use the tip of the tool to apply pressure on the corner of the lips, pushing up the tool. Repeat the massage three times.

